{"tid":1174931,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"封殺華為再一家！高通證實：手機、PC晶片全面停止供貨","createTime":"2019-05-28T08:09:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-28T08:42:35.000Z","uid":32511,"like":36,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"44c0d54ee1744e4624ae3dcc27b2a4e0c7785e66","tid":1174931,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T08:09:05.000Z","msg":"華為風暴越滾越大，手機晶片龍頭高通也加入停止供貨行列，高通產品管理資深總監Miguel Nunes今日表示，按照美國禁令規定，高通手機與PC平台晶片都已停止供貨給華為，但希望禁令解除後，可以再度合作。<br />\n<br />\n封殺華為的廠商不斷增加，繼安謀、美光等國際大廠，手機晶片龍頭高通也證實，依照美國禁令規定，目前已全面停止供貨給華為，包括手機、PC平台晶片均停止供應。"},{"pid":"63820c7d4006d4a4cb20b989b27c0c26dc6a9c7a","tid":1174931,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T08:14:17.000Z","msg":"又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"492b5d4c66c34bc413f3c922c7edddcf7689266f","tid":1174931,"uid":44358,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T08:15:37.000Z","msg":"中興應該偷笑緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"985d42ccc3ed37048637862ffbc7025162dd20f9","tid":1174931,"uid":31186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T08:16:11.000Z","msg":"華為又強大了一分"},{"pid":"5fba3b9afbd5d0e875ef0b8ff1aca5d43c9f6af3","tid":1174931,"uid":253954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T08:16:56.000Z","msg":"幾時到台積電<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05d2e5d81c86f97f951df860fbcdc2940d91014b","tid":1174931,"uid":20867,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T08:23:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://d13ezvd6yrslxm.cloudfront.net/wp/wp-content/images/Avengers-Endgame-portals-700x371.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd13ezvd6yrslxm.cloudfront.net%2Fwp%2Fwp-content%2Fimages%2FAvengers-Endgame-portals-700x371.jpg&h=da422bc5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3835a39d547f66f64d6e1a940e5ac3a650b18dc1","tid":1174931,"uid":19126,"like":0,